<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALM LATITUDES: VERBATIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 From an ad in the Placentia-based magazine American Survival Guide, which 
bills itself as the Magazine of Self Reliance: 
</P>
<P>
 For those of us living under the shadow of gun contol. . . 
</P>
<P>
 Hide your weapons WHILE YOU CAN! 
</P>
<P>
 GROUNDHOG (tm) UNDERGROUND STORAGE SYSTEMS 
</P>
<P>
 GROUNDHOD (tm) is the only container available today that will accept the 
AR15-M16 family of weapons without disassembly. . .the Groundhog (tm) easily 
holds four AR15s, two AK-47s and 2300 rounds of ammo, with extra room for 
handguns or anything else you want to safeguard. 
</P>
<P>
 DON'T LET THEM BURY YOUR RIGHT TO KEEP AND BEAR ARMS. 
</P>
</TEXT>
