<P>
BRIEFLY: SCHOOLS: LIBRARY WILL BE RENAMED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Mar Vista school library will be renamed in honor of the school's former 
principal. 
</P>
<P>
 Ella M. Hedler, 95, served as principal of Grand View Elementary School from 
1953 to 1965. On Monday, the student body will honor her in a dedication 
ceremony. 
</P>
<P>
 Hedler now lives in Iowa. Her retirement in 1965 marked the end of a teaching 
career that began in 1939. 
</P>
