<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTH: SOUTH-CENTRAL; HOUSING SERVICES FACILITY TO OPEN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Los Angeles Neighborhood Housing Services will open its new corporate 
headquarters in South-Central on Election Day. 
</P>
<P>
 The facilities at 3111 S. Flower St. will provide training for homeownership, 
financial and insurance counseling, loans to buy homes and for home 
rehabilitation, and youth training and employment. An 11:30 a.m. reception will 
be followed by an open house. 
</P>
<P>
 The 10-year-old nonprofit organization, which operates in four inner-city 
neighborhoods in Los Angeles, encourages residents to become stake holders in 
their community by assisting them to move from renter to homeowner. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (213) 749-7797. 
</P>
