<P>
 Saturday's scheduled games were St. John Bosco vs. Loyola at Glendale, and 
Bell-Jeff at Cathedral and La Salle vs.Salesian at Roosevelt. Jordan had a bye. 
Results of those games were unavailable for publication in City Times. See 
Sports, Section C. 
</P>
