<HEADLINE>
<P>
2 VIEWS ON THE LEASE LAW IN SAN FERNANDO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Yes, as you say in your Oct. 23 editorial "San Fernando's Ridiculous Lease 
Law," our city is only 2.4 square miles. This is exactly why we have to have a 
law to protect what little city property we now have, particularly the property 
in question. 
</P>
