<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOUTHLAND ROUNDUP; SOUTHERN UTAH BEATS NORTHRIDGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Southern Utah, 4-5 overall and 1-1 in the American West Conference, scored 
three second-quarter touchdowns in a 45-20 victory over Cal State Northridge 
(3-5, 0-2) Saturday at Southern Utah. . . . Darren MacLellan rushed for 295 
yards and four touchdowns for La Verne, 8-0 overall and 5-0 in Southern 
California Intercollegiate Athletic Conference, in a 45-22 conference win over 
host Claremont-Mudd (2-6, 1-4). Claremont's John Shipp passed for 349 yards and 
two scores. . . . Matt Figueroa rushed for 146 yards and one touchdown for 
Redlands (5-2-1, 4-1 in SCIAC) in a 30-6 conference victory over visiting 
Occidental (6-2, 4-1). 
</P>
