<P>
BUENA IN PLAYOFFS, SINKS DOS PUEBLOS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Buena High defeated Dos Pueblos, 10-5, Saturday in a third place tiebreaker 
match for the Channel League's final automatic berth in the Southern Section 
Division IV water polo playoffs. 
</P>
<P>
 Matt Swartout and Jeff Malas each scored three goals for the Bulldogs (13-13) 
and goalie Curtis Tomlie had 17 saves. 
</P>
<P>
 Buena led, 5-0, but Dos Pueblos scored three consecutive goals before the 
Bulldogs pulled away. 
</P>
