<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 6, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 2; Column 1; View Desk 
</P>
